<br>
School, Congress, Work, Random hold ups at your local gas station where you stopped to get some gas by someone you went to school with, arent things you can just put down and go somewhere else if others there do things that are shitty except to a very limited extent.<br>
<br>
Now you can still use those examples anyway for the broader point of this thread.  If im in a business and I find out tis laundering money and other random illegal acts you bet im going to quit and go to the police.  Why?  Cause when it is found out I dont want to be arrested and considered part of the acts.  As i WOULD be.  Why does it seem all politicians considered liars and schemers?  Cause some are.  So what happens?  Guild by association.  The vast majority of the populace considers them all that way.  Why?  Cause they dont know them as persons and have no way of knowing which are which.  Guilt by association once more.  How about a schools sports team?  If your team steals the opponents teams playbook and uses that to win, are you going to hang around still?  I wouldnt.  If it ever becomes known youre going to get tagged along with everyone else in the team.  Staying says you accept and condone that as acceptable.  Once again, Guild by Association.<br>
<br>
Now if its ONE person in these examples the business wwould sure as hell fire the person as soon as they found out.  The politician is going to lose most of their credibility and eventually fade out of the populaces eye.  And the one cheater on the school sports team is gonna get the boot.<br>
<br>
If youre there with the gunman when he holds the 7-11 up are you going to be considered associated with them because you had gone to school with them?  not likely.  If the gunman is your best friend and youre with them almost every day are the police going ot investigate you?  Sure as hell they are.<br>
<br>
As to them being your friends, well I dont know abotu anyone else but I personally wouldnt want ot be friends with someone who is a complete jackass and griefs other people.  If one of my friends decided to become a bank robber or someone who held up 7-11's I would tell them they better stop or they can go find someone else to be their friend.  Im loyal to my friends.  I care a lot for my friends.  Someone who fucks over other people for their own gain or just to do it is NOT my friend. <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=143487">
